PRESIDENT John Magufuli has revoked the appointment of Deputy Minister for Health, Community Development, Gender, Elderly and Children, Dr Faustine Ndugulile. According to a statement released on Saturday evening and signed by the Director of Presidential Communications, Mr Gerson Msigwa, the Head of State appointed Siha MP Dr Godwin Mollel as his replacement. The statement further stated that Dr Mollel’s appointment took effect  on Saturday.